hysics::WorldPtr _world, sdf::ElementPtr _sdf)\r\n{\r\n\tstd::cout << _world->GetModel(\"KitchenTable\")->GetBoundingBox() << std::endl;\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nI also attached the KitchenTable model.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>The returned bounding box of a model is the one of its last collision, this might have been overlooked in this <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo/issue/841/bounding-box-selection-is-incorrect\" rel=\"nofollow\">issue</a>.</p>\n<p>Code snippet (world plugin in the Load method):</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite language-c++\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"kt\">void</span> <span class=\"n\">WorldPluginEx</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Load</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">physics</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">WorldPtr</span> <span class=\"n\">_world</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">sdf</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">ElementPtr</span> <span class=\"n\">_sdf</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"p\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">std</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">cout</span> <span class=\"o\">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class=\"n\">_world</span><span class=\"o\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"n\">GetModel</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;KitchenTable&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"o\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"n\">GetBoundingBox</span><span class=\"p\">()</span> <span class=\"o\">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class=\"n\">std</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">endl</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>I also attached the KitchenTable model.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "new", "version": {"name": "all", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/versions/225575.json"}}}, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2014-11-06T11:32:04.849747+00:00", "milestone": null,